title: Bostitch Office 3 Hole Punch, Durable Metal,Rubber Base, 12 Sheets, Black
description: With this 12-Sheet hole punch, no task is too much. This 3-hole punch punches up to 12 sheets of paper at once to keep your work flow moving. It's durable with the metal build so you can house this is any classroom or office common room. Keep your workspace tidy as the chip tray catches all paper fall-out and is easy to empty! Stability during use is highly important - that's why this classic 3-hole punch features a rubber base for Supreme stability. It's available in a classic color that matches the rest of the Bostitch konnect organization system. Features: punches 12 sheets at once with a 3-hole configurationall-metal constructioneasy-to-clean waste tray rubber base pad for stability available in four colors to match the Konnect line.
